It's actually very difficult but...

840
00:45:38,569 --> 00:45:42,672
Seeing them smile, having fun, laughing...

841
00:45:42,673 --> 00:45:46,375
made my heart very, very soft.

842
00:45:46,376 --> 00:45:47,778
It actually feels great.

843
00:45:47,978 --> 00:45:49,345
As a Korean,

844
00:45:49,346 --> 00:45:52,615
I think that introducing Filipino food to Koreans

845
00:45:52,616 --> 00:45:56,385
was truly an honour and a rewarding experience.

846
00:45:56,386 --> 00:45:58,554
Kumusta is our identity.

847
00:45:58,555 --> 00:46:00,223
It's Filipino identity.

848
00:46:00,224 --> 00:46:04,160
The very first thing that you'd hear

849
00:46:04,161 --> 00:46:06,830
when you meet a Filipino is...

850
00:46:07,297 --> 00:46:08,799
Kumusta.

851
00:46:09,099 --> 00:46:11,200
Finally, we're closing!

852
00:46:11,201 --> 00:46:12,702
Okay, let’s go!

853
00:46:12,703 --> 00:46:14,204
Let’s go, let’s go.

854
00:46:19,143 --> 00:46:20,676
Say bye-bye for the last time!

855
00:46:20,677 --> 00:46:24,881
Bye, Kumusta!

856
00:46:24,882 --> 00:46:25,915
We're closing?

857
00:46:25,916 --> 00:46:27,517
Okay!

858
00:46:27,518 --> 00:46:28,685
Alright.

859
00:46:35,359 --> 00:46:38,529
Thank you!

860
00:46:42,566 --> 00:46:44,734
Let's go!

861
00:46:44,735 --> 00:46:46,236
I still couldn’t reach it.

862
00:46:47,571 --> 00:46:51,340
[Until we meet again]

863
00:46:51,341 --> 00:46:54,812
[Until we meet again] [Kumusta, Signing Off]

864
00:47:44,761 --> 00:47:46,964
Will you join us for Season 2?

865
00:47:49,800 --> 00:47:51,235
Will we have a Season 2?

866
00:47:52,936 --> 00:47:53,704
If we do.

867
00:47:53,705 --> 00:47:54,770
If we do?

868
00:47:54,771 --> 00:47:57,039
If we do, well...

869
00:47:57,040 --> 00:47:59,675
[Kumusta]

870
00:47:59,676 --> 00:48:01,811
[Kumusta 2]

871
00:48:01,812 --> 00:48:06,583
[Kumusta 2] [Maybe..?]
